{"formula_pattern_rule_id": "FPR_0021", "formula": "小承氣湯", "formula_family": "承氣湯", "six_channel_scope": ["陽明病", "厥陰病"], "core_pattern": "陽明病類證", "core_symptoms": ["譫語", "潮熱", "發熱", "燥屎"], "core_pulse": ["滑而疾", "滑疾"], "associated_symptoms": ["汗多", "惡寒", "不大便", "不能食", "欲飲水", "噦", "微煩", "小便數", "下利"], "associated_pulse": [], "contraindications": [], "composition": [{"herb": "大黃", "dose_processing": "四兩，酒洗"}, {"herb": "厚朴", "dose_processing": "二兩，炙，去皮"}, {"herb": "枳實", "dose_processing": "三枚，大者，炙"}], "administration_notes": ["分溫二服。初服當更衣，不爾者盡飲之，若更衣者，勿服之。"], "modification_relations": [], "supporting_initial_rules": ["IR_SHL_0208_002", "IR_SHL_0209_002", "IR_SHL_0213_001", "IR_SHL_0214_001", "IR_SHL_0250_001", "IR_SHL_0374_001"], "supporting_clauses": ["SHL_SONGBEN_0208", "SHL_SONGBEN_0209", "SHL_SONGBEN_0213", "SHL_SONGBEN_0214", "SHL_SONGBEN_0250", "SHL_SONGBEN_0374"], "source_level": "inductive_from_original_clauses", "interpretation_warning": "核心證候為跨條文歸納結果；病機類術語（如營衛不和）屬後世歸納，非所有條文原文直述。", "consensus_score": 0.9, "release_level": "gold"}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0208_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0208", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["汗多", "發熱", "惡寒"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["微和胃氣"], "alternatives": ["大承氣湯"]}, "evidence_span": "陽明病，脈遲，雖汗出不惡寒者，其身必重，短氣，腹滿而喘，有潮熱者，此外欲解，可攻裏也。手足濈然汗出者，此大便已硬也，大承氣湯主之；若汗多，微發熱惡寒者，外未解也，其熱不潮，未可與承氣湯；若腹大滿不通者，可與小承氣湯，微和胃氣，勿令致大泄下。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小承氣湯」，證據強度：斟酌可用（可與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "可與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.893, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0209_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0209", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["不大便", "燥屎", "不能食", "欲飲水", "噦", "發熱"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": ["六七日"], "contraindications": ["不可與"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["攻之", "和之"], "alternatives": ["大承氣湯"]}, "evidence_span": "陽明病，潮熱，大便微硬者，可與大承氣湯，不硬者，不可與之。若不大便六七日，恐有燥屎，欲知之法，少與小承氣湯。湯入腹中，轉矢氣者，此有燥屎也，乃可攻之；若不轉矢氣者，此但初頭硬，後必溏，不可攻之，攻之必脹滿不能食也。欲飲水者，與水則噦。其後發熱者，必大便復硬而少也，以小承氣湯和之。不轉矢氣者，慎不可攻也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小承氣湯」，證據強度：給予（與）。本條同時載明禁忌「不可與」，用方須以該禁忌為前提。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": ["repair:contraindication_annotated:不可與"], "consensus_score": 0.833, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0213_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0213", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["陽明病"], "symptoms": ["譫語"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["小承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": [], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "陽明病，其人多汗，以津液外出，胃中燥，大便必硬，硬則譫語。小承氣湯主之。若一服譫語止者，更莫復服。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為小承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「小承氣湯主之」，證據強度：主治關係（主之）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.9, "prescription_strength": "主之", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.936, "release_level": "gold"}}
